Hotel.name: Rockwater Residences - Green Hills Samui by Rockwater

Description.Text:
Property Location
With a stay at Rockwater Residences in Koh Samui (Bo Put), you'll be convenient to Bangkok Hospital Samui and Phetch Buncha Thai Boxing Stadium. This 5-star villa is within close proximity of Chaweng Thai Boxing Stadium and Tesco Lotus Koh Samui.

Rooms
Make yourself at home in one of the 37 individually decorated guestrooms, featuring kitchens with full-sized refrigerators/freezers and stovetops. Your Select Comfort bed comes with down comforters and Egyptian cotton sheets. Rooms have private balconies. 32-inch LCD televisions with cable programming provide entertainment, while complimentary wireless Internet access keeps you connected. Private bathrooms have deep soaking bathtubs and rainfall showerheads.

Amenities
Pamper yourself with onsite facials or take in the view from a garden. This villa also features complimentary wireless Internet access, concierge services, and babysitting/childcare (surcharge). The shuttle (surcharge) will take you to the nearby beach or shopping center.

Dining
Meet other guests and eat at a complimentary reception. Full breakfasts are available daily for a fee.

Business, Other Amenities
Featured amenities include limo/town car service, dry cleaning/laundry services, and multilingual staff. For a surcharge, guests may use a roundtrip airport shuttle (available 24 hours) and a ferry terminal shuttle.
